name: BRITNEY'S  PEARS / BRITNEY S PEARS / BRITNEY  SPEARS
description: Ughhh...you lied to us Andrew! You said we were almost done. Last one I promise, promise (for now). What was that? Nothing...Nothing I didn't say anything. Ummmm...look Britney Spears is here! (A distraction...they bought it! Yes!) Poor Britney, that woman has been through so much in her life. Between the nightmare of the conservatorship that her family put on her to good god what have I done to her name! The nerve of me making a reference to her incredibly wonderful décolletage of pears. This. Is. The. English. Language. Folks. I'm not making this stuff up. Wait, I am, but not really. It's like I'm in a quantum field of language or another dimension. Oh thank god, the writing is getting better. Who wrote the previous 44 pages? Man, he's way too serious.
